00:09:57.750 --> 00:10:00.300 align:middle line:90%
at hands daily, you see.

00:10:00.300 --> 00:10:06.740 align:middle line:84%
So it contains elements of
both the scientific elements

00:10:06.740 --> 00:10:11.400 align:middle line:84%
