directly from the soul.

00:10:14.915 --> 00:10:17.040 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So let's talk
about that because you say,

00:10:17.040 --> 00:10:21.010 align:middle line:84%
it actually tells you about
the constitution of your soul.

00:10:21.010 --> 00:10:24.370 align:middle line:84%
Your hands can tell you about
the constitution of your soul.

00:10:24.370 --> 00:10:25.770 align:middle line:90%
What does that mean?

00:10:25.770 --> 00:10:28.780 align:middle line:90%
And what are you seeing?

00:10:28.780 --> 00:10:31.650 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: Regina,
We are eternal.

00:10:31.650 --> 00:10:33.810 align:middle line:90%
We are not this body.

00:10:33.810 --> 00:10:37.980 align:middle line:84%
If one looks at
hands long enough,

00:10:37.980 --> 00:10:44.500 align:middle line:84%
one can understand that,
actually, the soul is eternal.

00:10:44.500 --> 00:10:49.160 align:middle line:84%
It's full of knowledge and
awareness, and it's happy.

00:10:49.160 --> 00:10:50.350 align:middle line:90%
It's joyful.

00:10:50.350 --> 00:10:54.940 align:middle line:84%
But while we're covered with
the material body and a material

00:10:54.940 --> 00:11:03.140 align:middle line:84%
mind full of material needs
and encumbrances and wants,

00:11:03.140 --> 00:11:05.560 align:middle line:90%
we forget our eternal nature.

00:11:05.560 --> 00:11:10.090 align:middle line:84%
We forget our internal
awareness And we

00:11:10.090 --> 00:11:13.450 align:middle line:90%
look for happiness externally.

00:11:13.450 --> 00:11:18.130 align:middle line:84%
And actually, happiness
and blissfulness and joy

00:11:18.130 --> 00:11:23.000 align:middle line:84%
are contained within the
soul and the connection

00:11:23.000 --> 00:11:27.050 align:middle line:84%
with God, with the
higher intelligences.

00:11:27.050 --> 00:11:34.270 align:middle line:84%
And while we're embodied and we
identify with the material body,

00:11:34.270 --> 00:11:43.990 align:middle line:84%
that becomes something that we
completely are not aware of.

00:11:43.990 --> 00:11:46.270 align:middle line:84%
So the problem with
our society right

00:11:46.270 --> 00:11:51.846 align:middle line:84%
now is that we have been
taught that we are our body.

00:11:51.846 --> 00:11:53.010 align:middle line:90%
We are Black.

00:11:53.010 --> 00:11:53.810 align:middle line:90%
We are white.

00:11:53.810 --> 00:11:54.680 align:middle line:90%
We are German.

00:11:54.680 --> 00:11:56.410 align:middle line:90%
We are Italian.

00:11:56.410 --> 00:11:58.910 align:middle line:84%
But we're not any of
these things eternally.

00:11:58.910 --> 00:12:00.880 align:middle line:90%
We're not this body.

00:12:00.880 --> 00:12:04.480 align:middle line:84%
And so if someone understands
that ultimately, they're

00:12:04.480 --> 00:12:06.170 align:middle line:84%
not this body,
they're spirit soul,

00:12:06.170 --> 00:12:10.870 align:middle line:84%
they're eternal, just that
idea will help someone

00:12:10.870 --> 00:12:17.540 align:middle line:84%
to move forward and not take
the miseries of this world

00:12:17.540 --> 00:12:18.435 align:middle line:90%
so seriously.

00:12:18.435 --> 00:12:19.310 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:12:19.310 --> 00:12:23.480 align:middle line:84%
So you say that it shows
the constitutional nature

00:12:23.480 --> 00:12:25.610 align:middle line:90%
of the soul.

00:12:25.610 --> 00:12:26.840 align:middle line:90%
Tell us what constitutional--

00:12:26.840 --> 00:12:28.340 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: The
constitutional nature

00:12:28.340 --> 00:12:33.570 align:middle line:84%
of the soul, as seen from
a palmistic point of view,

00:12:33.570 --> 00:12:36.680 align:middle line:84%
is that the soul is
composed completely

00:12:36.680 --> 00:12:41.060 align:middle line:84%
of love, of devotion,
of what's called bhakti.

00:12:41.060 --> 00:12:45.710 align:middle line:84%
And the soul's nature
is to give service.

00:12:45.710 --> 00:12:49.320 align:middle line:84%
That is what makes the soul
happy, to be of service.

00:12:49.320 --> 00:12:53.720 align:middle line:84%
And the soul's nature
is pure humility.

00:12:53.720 --> 00:13:00.470 align:middle line:84%
When a person's soul is pure,
then they are naturally humble.

00:13:00.470 --> 00:13:02.910 align:middle line:90%
They're naturally tolerant.

00:13:02.910 --> 00:13:07.630 align:middle line:84%
They don't lament when they lose
things in the material world.

00:13:07.630 --> 00:13:10.793 align:middle line:84%
They don't even find that much
happiness when they gain things

00:13:10.793 --> 00:13:11.710 align:middle line:90%
in the material world.

00:13:11.710 --> 00:13:15.480 align:middle line:84%
They understand that the
most precious things are

00:13:15.480 --> 00:13:21.200 align:middle line:90%
love and devotion and service.

00:13:21.200 --> 00:13:23.330 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So that's when
the purity of the soul

00:13:23.330 --> 00:13:27.380 align:middle line:84%
is really coming through
the third-dimensional life

00:13:27.380 --> 00:13:29.940 align:middle line:90%
of the person that's embodied.

00:13:29.940 --> 00:13:33.470 align:middle line:84%
And sometimes we call
that a type of mastery

00:13:33.470 --> 00:13:36.260 align:middle line:84%
or a type of enlightenment
when a soul can

00:13:36.260 --> 00:13:38.290 align:middle line:90%
live purely through the body.

00:13:38.290 --> 00:13:42.070 align:middle line:84%
Do you see that in the hands
of people who do, do that?

00:13:42.070 --> 00:13:43.290 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Yes, yes.

00:13:43.290 --> 00:13:46.640 align:middle line:84%
In hands of men and
women who are saintly,

00:13:46.640 --> 00:13:50.990 align:middle line:84%
they move through this
world completely unattached

00:13:50.990 --> 00:13:54.393 align:middle line:84%
from the encumbrances
of this material world.

00:13:54.393 --> 00:13:56.310 align:middle line:84%
They use the facilities
of the material world,

00:13:56.310 --> 00:13:57.740 align:middle line:90%
but they're not attached.

00:13:57.740 --> 00:13:59.323 align:middle line:84%
It's attachment that
brings suffering.

00:13:59.323 --> 00:14:01.282 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So if you were
looking at their palms

00:14:01.282 --> 00:14:04.010 align:middle line:84%
just as a broad stroke, because
we don't have a saint here

00:14:04.010 --> 00:14:06.560 align:middle line:84%
present to read,
what would you say

00:14:06.560 --> 00:14:09.860 align:middle line:84%
the broad stroke of a hand that
is unencumbered would look like?

00:14:09.860 --> 00:14:12.000 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: They don't
have material desires.

00:14:12.000 --> 00:14:13.200 align:middle line:90%
There's no lust.

00:14:13.200 --> 00:14:14.400 align:middle line:90%
There's no greed.

00:14:14.400 --> 00:14:16.285 align:middle line:90%
There's no envy.

00:14:16.285 --> 00:14:17.670 align:middle line:90%
They're free from this.

00:14:17.670 --> 00:14:18.930 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And so that
would show in the hands.

00:14:18.930 --> 00:14:19.950 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: That
shows in the hands.

00:14:19.950 --> 00:14:20.867 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Interesting.

00:14:20.867 --> 00:14:26.100 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: And let's say the
most difficult hands to look

00:14:26.100 --> 00:14:30.810 align:middle line:84%
at sometimes in
the way of people

00:14:30.810 --> 00:14:34.410 align:middle line:84%
not having faith in
the spiritual aspects

00:14:34.410 --> 00:14:39.820 align:middle line:84%
is that they're covered by lust
and greed and anger, you see.

00:14:39.820 --> 00:14:42.752 align:middle line:84%
Anger is the opposite
of love, you see.

00:14:42.752 --> 00:14:43.552 align:middle line:90%
So--

00:14:43.552 --> 00:14:44.860 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: And all this shows up.

00:14:44.860 --> 00:14:45.943 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: All this-- yes.

00:14:45.943 --> 00:14:46.950 align:middle line:90%
And you can see--

00:14:46.950 --> 00:14:49.290 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: OK, so you mentioned
something a little bit

00:14:49.290 --> 00:14:51.600 align:middle line:84%
ago, which I had
never thought of.

00:14:51.600 --> 00:14:55.030 align:middle line:84%
And I want to
