But at the same
time, it's temporary.

00:15:58.850 --> 00:16:00.850 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, that's
just this little glimpse.

00:16:00.850 --> 00:16:04.220 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: It's going to change
