00:16:47.290 --> 00:16:52.720 align:middle line:84%
Our activities in
this life directly

00:16:52.720 --> 00:16:56.560 align:middle line:84%
affect what we're doing in
this life and the next life.

00:16:56.560 --> 00:16:58.795 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well,
and actually, there

00:16:58.795 --> 00:17:00.670 align:middle line:84%
are a lot of people do
take kind of exception

00:17:00.670 --> 00:17:02.810 align:middle line:84%
to that notion thinking,
well, wait a minute.

00:17:02.810 --> 00:17:07.010 align:middle line:84%
But if you have done something
that is out of integrity,

00:17:07.010 --> 00:17:09.880 align:middle line:84%
unkind to another
soul or a group

00:17:09.880 --> 00:17:13.130 align:middle line:84%
of souls, that lowers your
vibrational frequency.

00:17:13.130 --> 00:17:16.430 align:middle line:84%
Everything is just
frequency, right?

00:17:16.430 --> 00:17:17.430 align:middle line:90%
And so you're going to--

00:17:17.430 --> 00:17:17.910 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: It's good question.

00:17:17.910 --> 00:17:19.710 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: You're going to find
a match for that frequency

00:17:19.710 --> 00:17:21.210 align:middle line:90%
in the next incarnation?

00:17:21.210 --> 00:17:23.910 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: Yeah,
and the idea here

00:17:23.910 --> 00:17:27.280 align:middle line:84%
is that if we go
through suffering,

00:17:27.280 --> 00:17:30.810 align:middle line:84%
we perpetrated suffering
on ourselves or others

00:17:30.810 --> 00:17:34.380 align:middle line:84%
before that, otherwise,
it's impossible for us

00:17:34.380 --> 00:17:36.970 align:middle line:84%
to suffer if we didn't
perpetrate that.

00:17:36.970 --> 00:17:42.850 align:middle line:84%
The demigods and the goddesses
are delineating our karma,

00:17:42.850 --> 00:17:47.890 align:middle line:84%
both good and bad, what we call
in Sanskrit akarma or moksha

00:17:47.890 --> 00:17:50.620 align:middle line:90%
karma or pious karma, akarma.

00:17:50.620 --> 00:17:54.630 align:middle line:84%
In other words, if
someone is going

00:17:54.630 --> 00:17:57.910 align:middle line:84%
through collective suffering
or their own suffering,

00:17:57.910 --> 00:18:00.880 align:middle line:84%
it's better just to
tolerate it and let it go.

00:18:00.880 --> 00:18:06.880 align:middle line:84%
That's the best way to deal
with difficult situations,

00:18:06.880 --> 00:18:10.030 align:middle line:84%
to just be tolerant, be
humble, and let it go.

00:18:10.030 --> 00:18:12.238 align:middle line:90%
Don't react, you see.

00:18:12.238 --> 00:18:13.780 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah,
that's the challenge.

00:18:13.780 --> 00:18:15.113 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: That's the challenge.

00:18:15.113 --> 00:18:18.970 align:middle line:84%
And of course, that has
to do with how advanced

00:18:18.970 --> 00:18:22.750 align:middle line:90%
a person is as a soul, you see.

00:18:22.750 --> 00:18:27.430 align:middle line:84%
An advanced soul will say, hey,
I perpetrated this suffering

00:18:27.430 --> 00:18:29.720 align:middle line:84%
on myself or others
in a previous life.

00:18:29.720 --> 00:18:34.970 align:middle line:84%
So let me just tolerate it, be
happy, and just move forward.

00:18:34.970 --> 00:18:36.400 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: That's
a very good point

00:18:36.400 --> 00:18:38.410 align:middle line:90%
