00:19:08.970 --> 00:19:14.130 align:middle line:84%
And it makes one actually
very aware of what's actually

00:19:14.130 --> 00:19:17.460 align:middle line:84%
going on deeper behind
the scenes internally

00:19:17.460 --> 00:19:18.780 align:middle line:90%
and externally.

