had struggles with, let's say,

00:19:28.110 --> 00:19:32.180 align:middle line:84%
their father, or the father
was absent or difficult to work

00:19:32.180 --> 00:19:32.980 align:middle line:90%
with.

00:19:32.980 --> 00:19:37.230 align:middle line:84%
