it has to do with the fact

00:19:37.230 --> 00:19:43.710 align:middle line:84%
that they were an absent
father or a difficult father

00:19:43.710 --> 00:19:44.830 align:middle line:90%
in their previous life.

00:19:44.830 --> 00:19:47.410 align:middle line:84%
So they have to taste
the results of that.

00:19:47.410 --> 00:19:52.810 align:middle line:84%
So hopefully, my job is to
say, hey, when you get older,

00:19:52.810 --> 00:19:54.070 align:middle line:90%
be a good dad.

00:19:54.070 --> 00:19:55.140 align:middle line:90%
Be a good mom.

00:19:55.140 --> 00:19:57.400 align:middle line:90%
And break the cycle, you see.

00:19:57.400 --> 00:20:00.720 align:middle line:84%
The whole point of suffering
actually is for purification.

00:20:00.720 --> 00:20:02.380 align:middle line:84%
That's the reason
in this material.

00:20:02.380 --> 00:20:03.820 align:middle line:90%
That's what we see in the hand.

