>>REGINA: You slot in
where your vibrations are.

00:20:47.440 --> 00:20:49.610 align:middle line:90%
So I like the way you put that.

00:20:49.610 --> 00:20:50.410 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Exactly.

00:20:50.410 --> 00:20:51.730 align:middle line:90%
And if someone sees--

00:20:51.730 --> 00:20:54.710 align:middle line:84%
and obviously, it's difficult
in this day and age.

00:20:54.710 --> 00:20:57.490 align:middle line:84%
But if someone sees
God in the universe

00:20:57.490 --> 00:21:00.700 align:middle line:84%
as friendly and favorable,
hey, whatever I'm going through

00:21:00.700 --> 00:21:02.830 align:middle line:90%
is for my benefit, good and bad.

00:21:02.830 --> 00:21:05.860 align:middle line:84%
If good stuff happens to
me, I offer the results

00:21:05.860 --> 00:21:07.910 align:middle line:90%
to God and others.

00:21:07.910 --> 00:21:10.120 align:middle line:84%
And if bad stuff
happens to me, I'll

00:21:10.120 --> 00:21:12.770 align:middle line:90%
tolerate it and try to learn.

00:21:12.770 --> 00:21:14.240 align:middle line:90%
Hey, what's the lesson here?

00:21:14.240 --> 00:21:18.340 align:middle line:84%
And that person moves through
life with peace and balance

00:21:18.340 --> 00:21:20.260 align:middle line:90%
and harmony, you see.

00:21:20.260 --> 00:21:21.880 align:middle line:90%
They don't blame others.

00:21:21.880 --> 00:21:23.840 align:middle line:90%
They blame themselves, you see

00:21:23.840 --> 00:21:24.640 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yes.

00:21:24.640 --> 00:21:29.500 align:middle line:84%
[LAUGHS] OK, so you say you
can see also the three--

00:21:29.500 --> 00:21:32.480 align:middle line:84%
going back to the functional
component part of the story,

00:21:32.480 --> 00:21:35.440 align:middle line:84%
you can see three
distinct components

00:21:35.440 --> 00:21:36.770 align:middle line:90%
of the soul in the hands.

00:21:36.770 --> 00:21:38.060 align:middle line:90%
What are those components?

00:21:38.060 --> 00:21:41.660 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: In Sanskrit, it's
called sat-chit-ananda--

00:21:41.660 --> 00:21:45.520 align:middle line:84%
knowledge, joyfulness,
and eternality.

00:21:45.520 --> 00:21:48.860 align:middle line:84%
And that is the
composition of the soul,

00:21:48.860 --> 00:21:51.680 align:middle line:90%
pure love, pure devotion.

00:21:51.680 --> 00:21:58.690 align:middle line:84%
The constitutional makeup of
the soul is absolute love.

00:21:58.690 --> 00:22:02.240 align:middle line:84%
And so when one advances
in consciousness,

00:22:02.240 --> 00:22:03.820 align:middle line:84%
they realize that,
actually, if I

00:22:03.820 --> 00:22:09.060 align:middle line:84%
do things in love and
devotion, I will become happy,

00:22:09.060 --> 00:22:13.480 align:middle line:84%
and I will have a good
effect upon others.

00:22:13.480 --> 00:22:22.330 align:middle line:84%
And the soul is not just
some energy or some--

00:22:22.330 --> 00:22:24.680 align:middle line:84%
it's not just some
ball of energy.

00:22:24.680 --> 00:22:26.500 align:middle line:90%
It's not just a ball of light.

00:22:26.500 --> 00:22:29.230 align:middle line:84%
In the spiritual
world, we actually

00:22:29.230 --> 00:22:33.200 align:middle line:84%
have a form, just like we have
a body now, but it's temporary.

00:22:33.200 --> 00:22:36.080 align:middle line:84%
It's subject to birth and
death and disease and old age.

00:22:36.080 --> 00:22:40.520 align:middle line:84%
In the spiritual world, we
actually have an eternal form.

00:22:40.520 --> 00:22:43.810 align:middle line:84%
We could be a boy or a
girl or a man or a woman

00:22:43.810 --> 00:22:49.930 align:middle line:84%
or a great gandharva,
demigod, or something.

00:22:49.930 --> 00:22:52.250 align:middle line:90%
But that form never changes.

00:22:52.250 --> 00:22:56.050 align:middle line:84%
It never goes through death
or old age or disease.

00:22:56.050 --> 00:22:58.520 align:middle line:90%
And that's an eternal form.

00:22:58.520 --> 00:22:59.920 align:middle line:90%
So that's the goal.

00:22:59.920 --> 00:23:02.170 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And you can see
those three components again

00:23:02.170 --> 00:23:04.095 align:middle line:84%
in the poem that you
were talking about.

00:23:04.095 --> 00:23:06.470 align:middle line:84%
These are the three components
of the soul recognizable--

00:23:06.470 --> 00:23:07.275 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Oh, absolutely,

00:23:07.275 --> 00:23:07.670 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: --in the palm.

00:23:07.670 --> 00:23:08.530 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Absolutely.

00:23:08.530 --> 00:23:09.330 align:middle line:90%
Absolutely.

00:23:09.330 --> 00:23:12.040 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So you can see what
level of development a person's

00:23:12.040 --> 00:23:13.990 align:middle line:90%
at on the soul level.

00:23:13.990 --> 00:23:15.035 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Absolutely.

00:23:15.035 --> 00:23:23.240 align:middle line:84%
Because the soul
is also emitting

00:23:23.240 --> 00:23:28.890 align:middle line:84%
knowledge of previous lives
and what this life is about.

00:23:28.890 --> 00:23:35.520 align:middle line:84%
So it's the repository of where
we've been and where we're going

00:23:35.520 --> 00:23:37.270 align:middle line:90%
and what we're here to achieve.

00:23:37.270 --> 00:23:42.700 align:middle line:84%
So in that way, the soul shows
its eternality in that aspect

00:23:42.700 --> 00:23:43.500 align:middle line:90%
also.

00:23:43.500 --> 00:23:44.890 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah,
that's wonderful.

00:23:44.890 --> 00:23:48.410 align:middle line:84%
OK, so one of the big
things people want to know--

00:23:48.410 --> 00:23:50.600 align:middle line:84%
and it can happen at
any age where they've

00:23:50.600 --> 00:23:51.660 align:middle line:90%
gone through their lives.

00:23:51.660 --> 00:23:54.050 align:middle line:84%
They've taken responsibility,
paid the bills.

00:23:54.050 --> 00:23:57.410 align:middle line:84%
And even at retirement,
the retired and it's still,

00:23:57.410 --> 00:23:58.920 align:middle line:84%
I just don't know
what I'm here for.

00:23:58.920 --> 00:24:01.010 align:middle line:84%
I just don't know what
I'm supposed to do.

00:24:01.010 --> 00:24:04.910 align:middle line:84%
How advantageous might it
be if your parents could

00:24:04.910 --> 00:24:06.500 align:middle line:84%
have a glimpse into
what you were here

00:24:06.500 --> 00:24:09.150 align:middle line:84%
to do before this
whole journey begins?

00:24:09.150 --> 00:24:11.930 align:middle line:84%
Because you say,
you can see what

00:24:11.930 --> 00:24:16.774 align:middle line:84%
your dharma is, what your
true expression in life

00:24:16.774 --> 00:24:19.740 align:middle line:90%
is in the palms, in your hands.

00:24:19.740 --> 00:24:20.540 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Yes.

00:24:20.540 --> 00:24:22.058 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So your life purpose.

00:24:22.058 --> 00:24:23.600 align:middle line:84%
So let's talk about
that for a moment

00:24:23.600 --> 00:24:25.430 align:middle line:84%
and give us a couple
examples of people

00:24:25.430 --> 00:24:27.950 align:middle line:84%
you've read, maybe when
they were a little younger,

00:24:27.950 --> 00:24:29.522 align:middle line:90%
and saw how it turned out later.

00:24:29.522 --> 00:24:30.980 align:middle line:10%
>>MAHABAL: Well,
that's interesting

00:24:30.980 --> 00:24:36.150 align:middle line:10%
because in our culture, our
careers change so often,

00:24:36.150 --> 00:24:37.530 align:middle line:10%
sometimes every 10 years.

00:24:37.530 --> 00:24:42.830 align:middle line:10%
When you look at someone or
you look at hands from old palm

00:24:42.830 --> 00:24:46.580 align:middle line:10%
prints made out of
ink and like that,

00:24:46.580 --> 00:24:49.890 align:middle line:10%
you see people who
grew up on a farm.

00:24:49.890 --> 00:24:51.530 align:middle line:90%
Their parents trained them.

00:24:51.530 --> 00:24:56.040 align:middle line:84%
And they work with alfalfa or
wheat the rest of their life,

00:24:56.040 --> 00:24:58.670 align:middle line:84%
or they work with a
lathe their entire life.

00:24:58.670 --> 00:25:03.770 align:middle line:84%
We see that in hands that are
100, 200 years old, let's say,

00:25:03.770 --> 00:25:04.893 align:middle line:90%
prints, hand prints.

00:25:04.893 --> 00:25:05.810 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Interesting.

00:25:05.810 --> 00:25:08.600 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: People learn their
trade from their parents,

00:25:08.600 --> 00:25:11.310 align:middle line:84%
and they continued on that
throughout their lives.

00:25:11.310 --> 00:25:13.380 align:middle line:84%
And in this culture, it's
completely different.

00:25:13.380 --> 00:25:16.693 align:middle line:84%
It's like every 10 years, a
person can change a career.

00:25:16.693 --> 00:25:17.860 align:middle line:90%
And we have to look at that.

00:25:17.860 --> 00:25:20.320 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So do our
hands look schizophrenic?

00:25:20.320 --> 00:25:21.970 align:middle line:90%
But let's hold on a minute here.

00:25:21.970 --> 00:25:25.240 align:middle line:84%
So your family
does raise alfalfa.

00:25:25.240 --> 00:25:28.710 align:middle line:84%
So you're born into this family,
and your prints are showing.

00:25:28.710 --> 00:25:31.510 align:middle line:84%
You're here to also
continue in the tradition.

00:25:31.510 --> 00:25:35.040 align:middle line:84%
So now you come to a world
that's corporate driven, where

00:25:35.040 --> 00:25:39.250 align:middle line:84%
in corporate world, your
skills are salesmanship,

00:25:39.250 --> 00:25:41.080 align:middle line:84%
maybe, or just keeping
things organized.

00:25:41.080 --> 00:25:42.790 align:middle line:90%
They're not so distinct.

00:25:42.790 --> 00:25:45.450 align:middle line:84%
And you can move around
even every few years

00:25:45.450 --> 00:25:48.090 align:middle line:84%
if you want to in
the corporate world.

00:25:48.090 --> 00:25:49.660 align:middle line:90%
How does that show in a hand?

00:25:49.660 --> 00:25:52.920 align:middle line:84%
Because it's not exactly
necessarily a dharma,

00:25:52.920 --> 00:25:55.240 align:middle line:84%
that you have leadership
skills maybe, the dharma.

00:25:55.240 --> 00:25:57.660 align:middle line:84%
But most people working
in the corporate world,

00:25:57.660 --> 00:26:02.140 align:middle line:84%
is that their dharma or for the
state government or whatever?

00:26:02.140 --> 00:26:05.745 align:middle line:84%
How does that look in the
palms now of modern society?

00:26:05.745 --> 00:26:07.480 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: Well, I
have to say, Regina,

00:26:07.480 --> 00:26:12.182 align:middle line:84%
that most of the people I look
at are not in the right careers.

00:26:12.182 --> 00:26:14.140 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well, that's
why I'm asking you this.

00:26:14.140 --> 00:26:15.670 align:middle line:90%
That's what I would guess.

00:26:15.670 --> 00:26:19.590 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: They're doing careers
that they're not born to do

00:26:19.590 --> 00:26:21.760 align:middle line:90%
or acclimated so well to do.

00:26:21.760 --> 00:26:24.510 align:middle line:84%
And it's because our
society waylays us

00:26:24.510 --> 00:26:27.295 align:middle line:84%
from doing the work
that we're here to do.

00:26:27.295 --> 00:26:28.170 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:26:28.170 --> 00:26:31.205 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: And that's
also very difficult, too.

00:26:31.205 --> 00:26:36.831 align:middle line:84%
And that has everything to do
with that we're not really--

00:26:36.831 --> 00:26:42.182 align:middle line:84%
our society is not really
that grounded in that way.

00:26:42.182 --> 00:26:43.640 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Well,
the whole structure

00:26:43.640 --> 00:26:45.260 align:middle line:90%
is ordered toward profit.

00:26:45.260 --> 00:26:47.750 align:middle line:84%
So how can you have
a grounded society

00:26:47.750 --> 00:26:50.043 align:middle line:84%
that's ordered toward
profit, profit, profit?

00:26:50.043 --> 00:26:51.210 align:middle line:90%
Doesn't matter where you go.

00:26:51.210 --> 00:26:54.270 align:middle line:84%
It's margins and profits,
whether it's, like I said,

00:26:54.270 --> 00:26:57.690 align:middle line:84%
governmental or corporate or
in corporatocracy in general.

00:26:57.690 --> 00:27:00.963 align:middle line:84%
Where is there room for a
person's soul expression

00:27:00.963 --> 00:27:02.880 align:middle line:84%
unless you claim it early
on and stay with it?

00:27:02.880 --> 00:27:04.380 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: It's
much harder with it.

00:27:04.380 --> 00:27:05.240 align:middle line:90%
It's much harder.

00:27:05.240 --> 00:27:10.610 align:middle line:84%
That's why in previous cultures
of hundreds and hundreds, maybe

00:27:10.610 --> 00:27:12.770 align:middle line:84%
even thousands of
years ago, people

00:27:12.770 --> 00:27:16.620 align:middle line:84%
would do their work that
they were born to do.

00:27:16.620 --> 00:27:18.980 align:middle line:84%
And they had time
for spiritual life.

00:27:18.980 --> 00:27:21.900 align:middle line:84%
They had time to
think, who am I?

00:27:21.900 --> 00:27:23.160 align:middle line:90%
What am I here to do?

00:27:23.160 --> 00:27:25.190 align:middle line:84%
They had time to
cultivate thoughts

00:27:25.190 --> 00:27:27.630 align:middle line:90%
of God and spirituality.

00:27:27.630 --> 00:27:31.970 align:middle line:84%
And in our culture, we're so
busy making a living at work

00:27:31.970 --> 00:27:38.240 align:middle line:84%
that we're not even
acclimated to do.

00:27:38.240 --> 00:27:40.165 align:middle line:90%
We lose our spiritual culture.

00:27:40.165 --> 00:27:41.040 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Absolutely.

00:27:41.040 --> 00:27:43.123 align:middle line:84%
So is this actually showing
up in people's hands--

00:27:43.123 --> 00:27:44.040 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Yes, it is.

00:27:44.040 --> 00:27:45.960 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: --this
schizophrenic way of living?

00:27:45.960 --> 00:27:48.190 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: Schizophrenic,
I like that.

00:27:48.190 --> 00:27:52.624 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: On a spiritual
level, it's schizophrenic.

00:27:52.624 --> 00:27:57.200 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: Yeah, I have to
say that the soul is general--

00:27:57.200 --> 00:28:00.720 align:middle line:90%


00:28:00.720 --> 00:28:07.950 align:middle line:84%
it is an entity that is god
conscious or goddess conscious.

00:28:07.950 --> 00:28:09.850 align:middle line:90%
That's just its nature.

00:28:09.850 --> 00:28:16.860 align:middle line:84%
But in our culture, we've
lost that natural inclination

00:28:16.860 --> 00:28:25.470 align:middle line:84%
to think of spiritual matters
because our leaders are bad

00:28:25.470 --> 00:28:26.380 align:middle line:90%
right now.

00:28:26.380 --> 00:28:29.790 align:middle line:84%
People don't know what
saintly qualities are.

00:28:29.790 --> 00:28:33.563 align:middle line:84%
There's not a lot of people
who have good examples.

00:28:33.563 --> 00:28:34.980 align:middle line:84%
There's not a lot
of good examples

00:28:34.980 --> 00:28:37.247 align:middle line:84%
of people who have morals
and standards and ethics.

00:28:37.247 --> 00:28:38.580 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: I couldn't agree more.

00:28:38.580 --> 00:28:39.880 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: That's the problem.

00:28:39.880 --> 00:28:41.990 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So here we are.

00:28:41.990 --> 00:28:43.570 align:middle line:90%
That's where we are right now.

00:28:43.570 --> 00:28:46.140 align:middle line:84%
But you said, too, that
in another five or six

00:28:46.140 --> 00:28:50.680 align:middle line:84%
years, once we start getting
out to 2030, '31, '32,

00:28:50.680 --> 00:28:53.130 align:middle line:84%
we're going to see
this vast change where

00:28:53.130 --> 00:28:58.480 align:middle line:84%
we start moving back into mind,
body, spirit as a way of living.

00:28:58.480 --> 00:29:02.810 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: That's because our
current society, as it is,

00:29:02.810 --> 00:29:05.258 align:middle line:90%
will go the way of the dinosaur.

00:29:05.258 --> 00:29:07.300 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: Yeah, because
we're going to reject it.

00:29:07.300 --> 00:29:08.300 align:middle line:90%
It's not working for us.

00:29:08.300 --> 00:29:09.467 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: It's not working.

00:29:09.467 --> 00:29:11.060 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: So in
another few years--

00:29:11.060 --> 00:29:13.220 align:middle line:84%
that's not that very
many years away--

00:29:13.220 --> 00:29:17.020 align:middle line:84%
my dream is to be able to see
people live their true dharma.

00:29:17.020 --> 00:29:19.060 align:middle line:84%
The thing that would
make me happiest

00:29:19.060 --> 00:29:22.060 align:middle line:84%
is that humanity shows
up, and each person

00:29:22.060 --> 00:29:25.360 align:middle line:84%
brings that natural talent and
skill of the thing they were

00:29:25.360 --> 00:29:27.820 align:middle line:90%
born to do through and lives.

00:29:27.820 --> 00:29:30.040 align:middle line:84%
Imagine the
complexity of society

00:29:30.040 --> 00:29:33.610 align:middle line:84%
and the peace that
would exist if everyone

00:29:33.610 --> 00:29:35.600 align:middle line:90%
did what they were born to do.

00:29:35.600 --> 00:29:36.400 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Exactly.

00:29:36.400 --> 00:29:37.200 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Yeah.

00:29:37.200 --> 00:29:40.195 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: And of course, I'm
a product of Western society,

00:29:40.195 --> 00:29:42.020 align:middle line:90%
and I love Western society.

00:29:42.020 --> 00:29:44.140 align:middle line:84%
But the problem
in Western society

00:29:44.140 --> 00:29:47.670 align:middle line:84%
is that it's based on
sense gratification.

00:29:47.670 --> 00:29:50.920 align:middle line:84%
It's based on eating
and sleeping and mating

00:29:50.920 --> 00:29:51.950 align:middle line:90%
and defending.

00:29:51.950 --> 00:29:55.120 align:middle line:84%
Whereas we look at the ancient
cultures and their culture

00:29:55.120 --> 00:29:59.193 align:middle line:84%
was based more on
spiritual principles.

00:29:59.193 --> 00:30:00.860 align:middle line:84%
They understood they
weren't their body.

00:30:00.860 --> 00:30:02.660 align:middle line:84%
They understood they
were spiritual soul.

00:30:02.660 --> 00:30:06.460 align:middle line:84%
So the entire foundation
of their society

00:30:06.460 --> 00:30:08.230 align:middle line:90%
was different than ours.

00:30:08.230 --> 00:30:09.290 align:middle line:90%
That's what's happening.

00:30:09.290 --> 00:30:10.190 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: So here we are.

00:30:10.190 --> 00:30:12.065 align:middle line:84%
I mean, we've gone
through industrialization,

00:30:12.065 --> 00:30:14.300 align:middle line:84%
and now we're watching
it start to decompose.

00:30:14.300 --> 00:30:15.100 align:middle line:90%
>>MAHABAL: Yes.

00:30:15.100 --> 00:30:16.517 align:middle line:84%
>>REGINA: And we're
going to watch

00:30:16.517 --> 00:30:18.160 align:middle line:84%
the resurgence of
our understanding

00:30:18.160 --> 00:30:21.640 align:middle line:84%
of an absolute need for
our mind, body, and spirit

00:30:21.640 --> 00:30:24.790 align:middle line:84%
to be integrated and offer
who we are to the planet.

00:30:24.790 --> 00:30:27.850 align:middle line:84%
Meanwhile, there are some
power spots on our hands

00:30:27.850 --> 00:30:31.690 align:middle line:84%
that also can be used to work
with our psychic and intuitive

00:30:31.690 --> 00:30:34.840 align:middle line:84%
forces, which we're needing
more and more because so

00:30:34.840 --> 00:30:37.010 align:middle line:84%
much of the world is
just a flat-out lie.

00:30:37.010 --> 00:30:40.820 align:middle line:84%
What we're being presented is
just fabrication, delusion,

00:30:40.820 --> 00:30:41.620 align:middle line:90%
lies.

00:30:41.620 --> 00:30:43.420 align:middle line:90%
All of us are sick of it.

00:30:43.420 --> 00:30:46.700 align:middle line:84%
We need to know how to use
