00:39:57.450 --> 00:40:04.400 align:middle line:84%
So I would say, these parents
should just say, try this.

00:40:04.400 --> 00:40:05.200 align:middle line:90%
Try that.

00:40:05.200 --> 00:40:06.130 align:middle line:90%
Try this.

00:40:06.130 --> 00:40:07.650 align:middle line:90%
Try that.

00:40:07.650 --> 00:40:12.126 align:middle line:84%
And think about what you
want to do for the future.

00:40:12.126 --> 00:40:13.980 align:middle line:84%
Don't put pressure
on them to try

00:40:13.980 --> 00:40:17.220 align:middle line:84%
to become successful
