00:40:17.220 --> 00:40:18.570 align:middle line:90%
happening right now.

00:40:18.570 --> 00:40:20.020 align:middle line:90%
>>REGINA: Excellent advice.

00:40:20.020 --> 00:40:23.850 align:middle line:84%
We have to keep in mind
this is the generation

00:40:23.850 --> 00:40:28.980 align:middle line:84%
that's been tasked with
starting this massive societal

00:40:28.980 --> 00:40:30.360 align:middle line:90%
restructuring.

00:40:30.360 --> 00:40:34.620 align:middle line:84%
As adults, they're going to
have to build these structures.

00:40:34.620 --> 00:40:38.640 align:middle line:84%
And we will inherit them when
we reincarnate in the future.

00:40:38.640 --> 00:40:42.000 align:middle line:84%
Gen Z is a very, very
important generation,

00:40:42.000 --> 00:40:43.750 align:middle line:84%
I think, the group
you're talking about.

00:40:43.750 --> 00:40:45.250 align:middle line:84%
