00:41:59.150 --> 00:42:00.460 align:middle line:90%
They've come to change things.

00:42:00.460 --> 00:42:01.750 align:middle line:84%
And of course, they're
going to feel out

00:42:01.750 --> 00:42:03.650 align:middle line:84%
of sorts while the
old is still in place.

00:42:03.650 --> 00:42:06.050 align:middle line:84%
But that's not going to
be in place much longer.

00:42:06.050 --> 00:42:08.710 align:middle line:84%
>>MAHABAL: And my prediction
is that when this--

00:42:08.710 --> 00:42:10.520 align:middle line:84%
